{"tid":761030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華富山坡驚現刀傷女屍","createTime":"2018-07-30T04:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T05:17:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"41759c477ccdaee303ab1ffd061c001267678b16","tid":761030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:56:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180730/20464121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F20464121&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4ktU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=924c3233\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F20464121&h=d3945f81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180730/20464121</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月30日 <br />\n<br />\n華富山坡驚現刀傷女屍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180730/large/0729lauwmimg_0006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180730%2Flarge%2F0729lauwmimg_0006.jpg&h=692394e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女子倒斃山坡，警員在場調查。劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名身有刀傷女子，昨晨被晨運人士發現倒斃在香港仔華富邨與華貴邨之間的山坡，警員在現場撿獲生果刀及遺書，惟沒有發現死者的身份證、銀包及手機，調查後相信案件無可疑，現正追查死者身份及尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n女死者年約40歲，身高約1.5至1.6米，當時身穿黑色上衣及黑色長褲，其頸、胸及雙手有刀傷，估計已死去一天，死因則有待法醫剖驗確定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑自刎後墮坡<br />\n<br />\n昨晨8時55分，華富邨街坊在華樂樓對開山坡晨運時，發現一名女子倒卧山坡全無反應，立即報警，警員及救護員到場證實女子已死去。由於她身有多處刀傷，又無身份證明文件，警方一度封鎖山坡調查，又調來機動部隊警員上山搜證。<br />\n<br />\n警員在女子身旁發現一個背囊及一把生果刀，背囊內有一封遺書，懷疑她以刀自刎後跌落山坡，但沒人察覺失救死去。警方調查後相信案件無可疑，正設法找尋其家人確定身份，仵工事後將屍體移送殮房。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉永明  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n維園塌樹椏壓傷兩印傭<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n伊院失誤聞所未聞　 肛門導管插陰道　婦須切輸卵管"},{"pid":"4b44cb5b4987ab4a402f8a0dad5c6f4f75b64a3b","tid":761030,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"睇錯華山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db710cfb054b8e2b4fe191f70801989e4ddc077","tid":761030,"uid":9566,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:05:04.000Z","msg":"我就覺得好有可疑囉"},{"pid":"b2a3d6c93681bbc7ab9294d9a899956fe6372e26","tid":761030,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:06:29.000Z","msg":"我以為係個叫華富山既人死撚左"},{"pid":"a80c8969d29c1d4969edf5d8fccddd5ad8213a9d","tid":761030,"uid":77355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2a3d6c93681bbc7ab9294d9a899956fe6372e26","tid":761030,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:06:29.000Z","msg":"我以為係個叫華富山既人死撚左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 低汁"},{"pid":"4be18dec0eff51725955b8196ccf5e36a70d46dc","tid":761030,"uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"多處刀傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係又自殺 都幾癲 自隊n下碌落山 咁痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d655a4708d672a4d9d540e55cee057e93a7851","tid":761030,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"正常人自殺都唔會隊咁多刀啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4644b8fc3d1ba9a1c25b75458451c58ffe80e26f","tid":761030,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:17:42.000Z","msg":"有遺書一定係自殺啦"}]}